Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

######## yash.3997@gmail.com ########
IMAPAccount FirstGmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User yash.3997@gmail.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup host smtp.gmail.com service smtp user yash.3997"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail1-remote
Account FirstGmail

MaildirStore gmail1-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail1/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail1/inbox

Channel gmail1-inbox
Master :gmail1-remote:
Slave :gmail1-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel gmail1-sent
Master :gmail1-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :gmail1-local:sent

Channel gmail1-trash
Master :gmail1-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :gmail1-local:trash

Group gmail1
Channel gmail1-inbox
Channel gmail1-sent
Channel gmail1-trash

